  "text": "Previous global modeling studies have focused on the effects of diffuse light on total carbon or net primary productivity. For example, [CITATION_1] quantify the spatially-varying effects of aerosols on carbon flux and productivity as a whole using a land-surface scheme along with AOD from a separate chemistry simulation, but they do not focus on crop production.",
